To clarify and examine the defect states and trap recombination at the HTL/perovskite interface, the space-charge limited current model is employed. The trap-state density (ntrap) can be calculated using the following relationship56,6ntrap=2εεoVTFLeL2,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
